				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">LDoN song lineup<a name="24000"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Feb 26 04 8:38 AM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>I've been on quite a few adventures with my necro but none with my bard.  She's lvl 34 and I'm wondering what kind of song lineup I should have memmed.  Should I be more of a singer or melee ( I know it depends on the group but this is a general question ).  Once I get going I will probably have a sing song group and a melee song group saved but like it said, I haven't been on any yet with the bard.  I just don't want to go in there and have a lute or brass in my hand and have people thinking I'm not doing my job because they don't see a big effect with 4 songs playing.  BTW, I have all songs up though the two 34 songs.  Thanks for your help.  If you have any questions for me, I'll answer them asap.
<br />

<br />
Edit:  I can deal a lot of damage since I have good weapons and I solo a lot but I know I shouldn't take agro from the tanks.</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
