				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: LDoN song lineup<a name="49727"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Jul 2 04 11:35 AM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>1) Winds of Marr... of course.
<br />
2) Warsong of Zek... gotta love DS, atk, haste and all that melee goodness
<br />
3) Call of the Muse... nothing like overhaste and nuke/dot focus
<br />
4) Psalm of Veeshan... resists and heavy stackable DS... yum yum
<br />

<br />
Not in the twist...
<br />

<br />
5) Requiem of Time... good for pulling, and nice to preslow any mob anyhow
<br />
6) Silent Song of Quellious... I always pull, so I always lull.
<br />
7) Brusco's Boastful Bellow... sometimes tap RoT and stop it too fast, and recast is slow, so bellow the mob before the lull wear off.
<br />
8) Lullaby of Morell... Gotta keep a mez handy. Never leaves my song lineup.
<br />

<br />
For Hard LDoN's, I keep Solons Charismatic Concord memmed in slot 7 for those extra paci resistant mobs who needs a tad more Cha to get paci'd.</span></td>
